Name: Megaspeed
Title: Baja 1000
Desc: Bryce Menzies attempts to win the one off-road event that has always eluded him, the Baja 1000.
LongDescription: Bryce Menzies attempts to win the one off-road event that has always eluded him, the Baja 1000; Barefoot Bobby Williams is out to capture the crown at the annual Swamp Buggy Championship.
